creator: e9ine Ltd
descriptionHtml:
This app is for drivers working for JAF Executive Travels. This app allows drivers to receive bookings and progress them using a simple interface.

The app allows drivers to be in control of their data. The app features include:
1. Driver Messaging
2. Dashboard
3. Bookings
4. Job Pool
5. Account Statements

Note: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: General bug fixes and UI Enhancements
